**Privacy Policy for CryptoDCA**
**Developer:** Appnovex
**Website:** [www.appnovex.com](http://www.appnovex.com)
**Effective Date:** December 20, 2025

CryptoDCA (“we,” “our,” or “the app”) respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your information.

**1. Data Collection**
CryptoDCA does **not collect, store, or share any personal information** from users. This includes, but is not limited to:

* Names, email addresses, phone numbers
* Location data
* Contacts or calendar information
* Device information or identifiers
* Usage data or analytics

**2. Third-Party Services**
This app does **not use any third-party services** that collect data. No advertising, analytics, or tracking frameworks are integrated.

**3. Cookies and Tracking**
The app does not use cookies, tracking pixels, or any tracking technologies.

**4. Children’s Privacy**
CryptoDCA does not knowingly collect information from children under 13. Since we do not collect any data, we comply with applicable children's privacy regulations.

**5. Changes to This Privacy Policy**
We may update this policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page. Your continued use of the app indicates acceptance of the updated policy.

**6. Contact Us**
If you have any questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy, you can contact us at: [support@appnovex.com]
